attributes.title: Dimensions of Sadashivoham 2016: Mallakambha & Rope Yoga
attributes.description: A yogic body means: power, flexibility, energy and health. With Mallakambha you will have power, with rope yoga you will have flexibility, with Kundalini awakening you will have energy and all these three will naturally make you healthy. All these are available at Sadashivoham 2016!
